         <div type="translation">
            <p>To the Divine Spirits [of - Pe]troni[ana, dea]rest [daughter] [who lived] for
               twenty-three [ye]ars. [- - Ma]crinus [(her) father, a veteran,] and Vale[ria -, (her)
               m]other (made this).</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Line 2: The gentilicium of the deceased (the feminine of her father’s) is
               missing.  </p>
            <p>Line 5: The abbreviation of the deceased’s father’s praenomen and his gentilicium are
               missing. </p>
            <p>Line 7: The deceased’s mother’s cognomen is missing. </p>
         </div>
